race.comment: NAILS MURPHY (4) is on the doorstep of another victory placing in four of his past five starts and this is not an overly strong affair. Gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. TANGO QUEEN (10) brings NSW formlines to the table but should be high on confidence following that last-start Newcastle win. Will give backers a sight. MORE TROUBLE (3) has won over this course and distance and strips fitter third-up from the spell. In the mix. ZOU BIG BOY (6) gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination and cannot be underestimated.
